graph LR
    DSPO[Data Science Pipelines<br/>Operator]

    %% External Dependencies - Required
    DSPO -->|pipeline execution| Tekton[OpenShift Pipelines<br/>Tekton 1.8+]
    DSPO -->|platform| K8s[OpenShift/Kubernetes<br/>4.9+]
    DSPO -->|metadata storage| MariaDB[MariaDB 10.x<br/>or External SQL]
    DSPO -->|artifact storage| S3[S3-compatible Storage<br/>Minio dev / AWS S3 prod]
    DSPO -->|external access auth| OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    DSPO -->|UI integration| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
    DSPO -->|metrics collection| Monitoring[OpenShift Monitoring<br/>ServiceMonitor]
    DSPO -->|external routes| Routes[OpenShift Routes]
    DSPO -->|TLS certs| ServiceCA[OpenShift Service CA]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard -->|API calls| DSPO
    Elyra[Elyra /<br/>kfp-tekton SDK] -->|submit pipelines| DSPO

    %% External Services
    DSPO -->|production storage| ExtS3[External S3<br/>AWS/Azure]
    DSPO -->|production DB| ExtDB[External Database<br/>MySQL/PostgreSQL]
    DSPO -->|task images| Registry[Container Registry<br/>Quay/etc]

    %% Tekton dependencies
    Tekton -->|executes| PipelineRuns[Tekton PipelineRuns]
    PipelineRuns -->|runs tasks| TaskPods[Pipeline Task Pods]
    TaskPods -->|artifacts| S3
    TaskPods -->|metadata| MLMD[ML Metadata<br/>optional]

    %% MLMD integration
    DSPO -.->|optional| MLMD
    MLMD -->|stores in| MariaDB

